Package com.intellij.execution.process

Class ProcessIOExecutorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutorService
      • java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor
        • com.intellij.execution.process.ProcessIOExecutorService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Executor, java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService

    public class ProcessIOExecutorService
extends java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor
    A thread pool for long-running workers needed for handling child processes or network requests, to avoid occupying workers in the main application pool and constantly creating new threads there.
